verses.verse: While I <S%H2416>live<s%> will I <S%H1984>praise<s%> the <S%H3068>LORD:<s%> I will <S%H2167>sing<s%> praises to my <S%H430>God<s%> <S%H5750>while<s%> I have any <S%H5750>being.<s%>
Put not your <S%H982>trust<s%> in <S%H5081>princes,<s%> nor in the <S%H1121>son<s%> of <S%H120>man,<s%> in whom there is <S%H369>no<s%> <S%H8668>help.<s%>
His <S%H7307>breath<s%> <S%H3318>goes<s%> <S%H3318>forth,<s%> he <S%H7725>returns<s%> to his <S%H127>earth;<s%> in that very <S%H3117>day<s%> his <S%H6250>thoughts<s%> <S%H6>perish.<s%>
<S%H835>Happy<s%> is he that has the <S%H410>God<s%> of <S%H3290>Jacob<s%> for his <S%H5828>help,<s%> whose <S%H7664>hope<s%> is in the <S%H3068>LORD<s%> his <S%H430>God:<s%>
Which <S%H6213>made<s%> <S%H8064>heaven,<s%> and <S%H776>earth,<s%> the <S%H3220>sea,<s%> and <S%H3605>all<s%> that therein is: which <S%H8104>keeps<s%> <S%H571>truth<s%> for <S%H5769>ever:<s%>

Which <S%H6213>executes<s%> <S%H4941>judgment<s%> for the <S%H6231>oppressed:<s%> which <S%H5414>gives<s%> <S%H3899>food<s%> to the <S%H7456>hungry.<s%> The <S%H3068>LORD<s%> <S%H5425>looses<s%> the <S%H631>prisoners:<s%>

The <S%H3068>LORD<s%> <S%H6491>opens<s%> the eyes of the <S%H5787>blind:<s%> the <S%H3068>LORD<s%> <S%H2210>raises<s%> them that are <S%H3721>bowed<s%> down: the <S%H3068>LORD<s%> <S%H157>loves<s%> the <S%H6662>righteous:<s%>

The <S%H3068>LORD<s%> <S%H8104>preserves<s%> the <S%H1616>strangers;<s%> he <S%H5749>relieves<s%> the <S%H3490>fatherless<s%> and <S%H490>widow:<s%> but the <S%H1870>way<s%> of the <S%H7563>wicked<s%> he <S%H5791>turns<s%> upside down.
The <S%H3068>LORD<s%> shall <S%H4427>reign<s%> for <S%H5769>ever,<s%> even your <S%H430>God,<s%> O <S%H6726>Zion,<s%> to all <S%H1755>generations.<s%> <S%H1984>Praise<s%> you the <S%H3050>LORD.<s%>
